title: Ultimate Power Hour: Super Hits 1994-1956
description:
*********** THE OTHER TORRENT IS MISSING TRACK 5 *********** 


For the "Power Hour" drinking game:
60 second excerpts from hits from 1994-1956.  I list the dates backwards because the tracks start at 1994 and work backwards chronologically from 1994-1956.  Track 60 is the only track out of chronological order, because it is the celebratory final track-- a full-length recording of "We Are The Champions" by Queen.

Enjoy, and be safe.
